{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"be63b68ec3","title":"浙江大学关于毕业设计问题的大字报","origin":"浙江大学马列主义教研室资料室编印《右派言论汇编（内部刊物）》，1957年11月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f07ddbf693","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"be63b68ec3"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"849666544f","type":"title","text":"浙江大学关于毕业设计问题的大字报","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"a05a9b14e4","type":"subtitle","text":"1、毕业设计问题","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"8ec0a49a52","type":"paragraph","text":"在毕业设计的过程中培养的不是独立工作能力，而是“懒惰”“不懂装懂”和“吹牛”！","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"b4966a004f","type":"paragraph","text":"毕业设计既不是学习的总结，更不是工程师工作的预习，而是誊公文工作的尝试！","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"03e9e1b7dc","type":"paragraph","text":"在这最后关头我们不能容忍下去了，我们要做时间的主人，立即行动起来挽救我们学生时代最后一个月的宝贵时间，毕业班同学们我们要团结起来，向教条主义开火！！！","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"91a492ad85","type":"paragraph","text":"我们建议尽快组成一代表团立即向校长请愿，坚决要求立即停止毕业设计！","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"0a3f131733","type":"subtitle","text":"2、劳命伤财的毕业设计应立即停止！","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"11778d5e28","type":"paragraph","text":"毕业设计洋八股　真象一间中药铺　工艺经济都包括","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"2416bd68c4","type":"paragraph","text":"外加保安与防火　序言部分离不掉　实际牛皮一大套","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"cbaed996a8","type":"paragraph","text":"国民经济重要性　五年计划里面抄　明明落后十几年","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"1c92bb7cc7","type":"paragraph","text":"还要把它来夸耀　计算失去真意义　硬凑答案真无聊","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"f1a4b0af01","type":"paragraph","text":"实验本是为效验　现在反把考门找　闭门造车做工艺","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"8c40ea8587","type":"paragraph","text":"厂里卡片原片抄　设计培养描图员　一笔一划照样抄","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"f7ac5e97a6","type":"paragraph","text":"这些害处真不少　浪费精力杜操劳　还是省下时间来","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"86f0fc12ee","type":"paragraph","text":"学习外文更重要　同学呼声催领导　齐心合力除教条！","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"d37bcfc7f9","type":"subtitle","text":"3、同意停止毕业设计","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"a9b5272e33","type":"paragraph","text":"（标题为编者所加）","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"cd037b01e8","type":"paragraph","text":"别再浪费我们宝贵的时间吧！我们一致同意光仪四，电机四的意见——立即停止毕业设计。总结我们的设计经验是：翻、抄、搬、套，再加上微不足道的独立思考。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"d0b95a78d6","type":"paragraph","text":"这就说明毕业设计是得不偿失的，没有意义的，应立即停止。把剩下来的二个月时间用来弥补4年来最大的缺陷——起码的外文基础及其础课。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"d113591ed1","type":"subtitle","text":"4、毕业设计","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"4e8049f4c4","type":"paragraph","text":"毕业设计真无聊，采暖通气样样要，","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"55e7353169","type":"paragraph","text":"经济核算少不了，东翻西翻抄资料，","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"},{"id":"0f945b45e3","type":"paragraph","text":"缺点多来优点少，劳命伤财遭透了。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3"}],"page":{"id":"21e3283b6e","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be63b68ec3","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}